text: Franz Aschenwald (11 January 1913 - 31 January 1945) was an Austrian ski jumper. He competed in the individual event at the 1936 Winter Olympics. ==References== Category:1913 births Category:1945 deaths Category:Austrian male ski jumpers Category:Olympic ski jumpers of Austria Category:Ski jumpers at the 1936 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Tyrol (state)
